title: Top Floor 1BR with Downtown Views from Northeast!
posting_body: ['The Julia is a boutique apartment building in the heart of Northeast, at the corner of Broadway and Marshall.', "Our next door neighbors are The 1029 Bar, and we're kitty-corner from the historic Grain Belt Building and Pierre Bottineau Library.", 'Young Joni and Dangerous Man are two (!) blocks away.', "In short, the location can't be beat -- and we think our building is pretty cool, too.", 'Our community features multiple state-of-the-art amenities including a stunning rooftop deck, 24-hour fitness center and efficient, upgraded unit interiors for your everyday life.', '#708 -- Plan M', 'Note, our online pricing shows the effective monthly rate when factoring in our current specials.', 'However, you would use the special up-front and pay regular market rent $1,725/mo. afterwards.', '.', 'Unit #708 is a one bedroom apartment located on the seventh floor.', 'It is finished with warm vinyl oak plank flooring, beautiful gray marbled quartz countertops and LED lighting throughout.', 'It features a full size high efficiency washer/dryer, a balcony with a skyline view and a smart, functional design.', 'Note: images are from a comparable unit', '.', 'For info on amenities and to apply: <URL>', 'For your Instagram fix: @solhemcompanies', 'The Julia is managed by locally-owned Solhem Companies: <URL>', 'Prices subject to change.', 'NE Mpls -- NE -- Northeast Minneapolis -- Northeast -- Nordeast -- Arts District -- U of M -- New Construction -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Large Dog Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging']
